ailist.AIList.unfreeze¶

AIList.unfreeze(self)¶

Make AIList mutable

Parameters
None

Returns

Return type

None

See also

AIList.freeze()

Make immutable

AIList.sort()

Sort intervals inplace

AIList.construct()

Construct AIList, required to call AIList.intersect

Examples

>>> from ailist import AIList
>>> ail = AIList()
>>> ail.add(1, 2)
>>> ail.add(3, 4)
>>> ail.add(3, 6)
>>> ail
AIList
  range: (1-6)
   (1-2, 0, 0.0)
   (3-4, 1, 0.0)
   (3-6, 2, 0.0)
>>> ail.freeze()
>>> ail.add(9, 10)
TypeError: AIList is frozen and currently immutatable. Try '.unfreeze()' to reverse.
>>> ail.unfreeze()
>>> ail.add(9, 10)
